{"tid":2388715,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《天賜的聲音》諷刺一幕：周傳雄當選手，孟美岐當導師！","createTime":"2021-01-31T10:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T09:01:32.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"36dac035f949dd1d8ec9d9575860e9837e4743bb","tid":2388715,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:41:57.000Z","msg":"這是一個流量為王的時代，甭管我們接不接受，這都是事實，你即便再有實力，曾經再紅，如果不具備流量，也只能是被淘汰，被遺忘，這不，在最新一期《天賜的聲音》中出現了諷刺一幕：周傳雄當選手，孟美岐當導師！<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0131%2Fad40e22fp00qnro7300dcc000jb00gec.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0131%252Fad40e22fp00qnro7300dcc000jb00gec.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=0a02e52f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0131%2Fc151923cp00qnro7300bic000o100hmc.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0131%252Fc151923cp00qnro7300bic000o100hmc.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=05bf25a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  與其喊周傳雄，不如說小剛，因為這是他出道之後的名字，也是大家記憶最深刻的兩個字，被業內譽為情歌教父的小剛有很多代表作，比如《我的心太亂》、《黃昏》、《寂寞沙洲冷》、《愛的告別式》等！<br />\n<br />\n  值得一提的是，小剛的《我的心太亂》是1996年發行的，那個時候，孟美岐還沒有出生！<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  24年後，孟美岐參加《創造101》C位出道，是火箭少女裡流量和人氣最高的，資源也是好到燙手！各大綜藝上不停，又是《演員請就位》，又是《天賜的聲音》<br />\n<br />\n  倒不是說孟美岐不好，她的職業態度和性格，都是值得我們點讚的，而是相比某些選手和導師，她的資格真的沒有達到這個級別，比如台下站著何潔、小剛，台上坐著胡彥斌、陶喆、張韶涵！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0131%2Fb51905aap00qnro7300c4c000kp00g6c.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0131%252Fb51905aap00qnro7300c4c000kp00g6c.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=bab03a05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0131%2F82aa2372p00qnro7300hjc000ot00iyc.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0131%252F82aa2372p00qnro7300hjc000ot00iyc.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=9fadea45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  慶幸的是，幾十年後，小剛老師依舊保持著出道時的樣子，聲音、體型都沒有什麼改變，只不過鬢邊的鬍子有些白了！"},{"pid":"37863792b6c0d0c24e7f32e7329eea77e6b9a0ba","tid":2388715,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:20:02.000Z","msg":"而家冇人識小剛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5eb0c93d6877e72224e9e5bd9c10ee3ef76416a","tid":2388715,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:16:09.000Z","msg":"憑乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60aac1f9d9481c8bcc34fd7e5cd513c5e13facb2","tid":2388715,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:52:43.000Z","msg":"個時咁紅<br />\n點解而家要做上台表現唔係評審<br />\n當佢新人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6c52cff2497e6f9ac222d54eb98d0f6d770bda","tid":2388715,"uid":261172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"佢以前同李克勤合唱隻天這樣藍都幾正<br />\n <br />\n雖然係奶共歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69399f4d5cd1edaae226aa5a7f7ae310a132eca7","tid":2388715,"uid":192358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:01:32.000Z","msg":"記事本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}